31:12.504 --> 31:17.490
Let it go, let it go, and let God work.

31:18.338 --> 31:27.788
You got to do that, but I'm telling you, when you let it go, even if it's unfair, it's unfair all the time, how many people have forgiven you because it was unfair?

31:30.090 --> 31:31.171
It's not about fairness.

31:31.812 --> 31:38.099
It wasn't fair for Jesus to die for us, but we received forgiveness for what he gave for us.

31:39.480 --> 31:40.361
