31:41.983 --> 31:45.266
Maybe this Christmas in the tension in your family.

31:45.986 --> 31:48.610
Or the tension with a friend or former friend.

31:50.732 --> 31:51.113
Let it go.

31:52.194 --> 31:53.236
Forgive them, release it.

31:54.798 --> 31:55.659
That is powerful.

31:57.221 --> 32:00.766
And you will have the peace repaired in your heart.

32:02.568 --> 32:02.909
Let it go.

32:04.150 --> 32:08.296
When you're holding on to that bitterness and resentment, you're only poisoning yourself.

32:08.797 --> 32:10.038
It's not hurting the other person.

32:10.759 --> 32:11.160
Let it go.

32:12.041 --> 32:14.585
Find peace with God through faith in Jesus.

32:14.845 --> 32:15.666
It's the only way.

32:16.706 --> 32:18.789
protect your peace by prayer.

32:19.249 --> 32:26.218
When you're feeling anxious, pray specifically about what you're feeling anxious about, and list a whole bunch of things you're grateful for.

32:26.718 --> 32:28.300
